attributes.description: This Golang dashboard visualizes Heap metrics.

panelsJSON.title: Heap GC summary over time [Metrics Golang]
Heap objects summary over time [Metrics Golang]

params.expression:
.es(q="event.dataset:golang.heap",index="logs*",metric="max:golang.heap.gc.pause.sum.ns").bars().label("Sum of GC pause duration(ns)").yaxis(label="Duration(ns)").color(lightblue),
.es(q="event.dataset:golang.heap",index="logs*",metric="max:golang.heap.gc.pause.total.ns").derivative().movingaverage(30).label("Total GC pause(ns) rate").color(green),
.es(q="event.dataset:golang.heap",index="logs*",metric="max:golang.heap.gc.pause.max.ns").label("Max GC pause(ns)").movingaverage(30).color(red),
.es(q="event.dataset:golang.heap",index="logs*",metric="avg:golang.heap.gc.pause.avg.ns").label("Avg GC pause(ns)").movingaverage(30).color(magenta),
.es(q="event.dataset:golang.heap",index="logs*",metric="max:golang.heap.gc.pause.count").condition(lt,1, null).label("GC pause count").yaxis(2,label="Count").color(orange).legend(position=ne)

attributes.title: [Metrics Golang] Heap
